<HEADLINE>
Immigrants avoiding beefed-up patrols to cross Mexican border
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; RETRANSMITTING to fix slug
 &UR; AP Photo LA101 &QL; 
 &UR; AP Graphic IMMIGRATION SHIFT &QL; 
 &UR; By MICHELLE KOIDIN &QC; 
