</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Australia-Pizza Delivery Killer </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Pizza delivery killer sentenced to mental institution
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   SYDNEY, Australia (AP) _ A pizza delivery man, who stabbed a
customer to death under the belief he was controlled by aliens, was
sentenced Tuesday to an indefinite stay in a mental hospital.
	   Robuen Barrioquito Diaz, 21, of Punchbowl, a Sydney suburb, had
pleaded innocent to murdering Edwina Leonora Powell, 20, on
September 17, 1996, and maliciously wounding her neighbor, Kenneth
Alan Breward.
	   New South Wales state Supreme Court judge Graham Barr found Diaz
innocent on the grounds that he did not know that what he was doing
was wrong.
	   ``This is a truly tragic case in which a gentle young man
without any criminal tendencies, affected by an illness over which
he had no control, attacked three innocent people and killed one of
them,'' Barr said.
	   Barr, who heard the trial without a jury, said three
psychiatrists who examined Diaz found that he suffered a psychotic
illness that began in about mid-1996.
	   During the trial the court heard that Diaz had told a nurse a
television set talked to him and told him a device had been planted
in his head so he could be controlled by alien forces.
	   Diaz told his mother he had been abducted by aliens, an
occurrence he said he discovered when his watch lost an hour, and
that aliens told him to write on a wall.
	   The judge said Diaz had written in blood on the wall of Powell's
unit after killing her.
	   The judge said that at various times before the killing, Diaz
had intended to jump off cliffs to his death, had been stopped from
throwing himself under a train and had been interrupted when trying
to hang himself.
	   Barr said Diaz will remain in a mental hospital indefinitely.
The state Mental Health Review Tribunal would review Diaz's case
regularly and make recommendations to the government about his
progress and possible future release. 	   
</TEXT>
(PROFILE
(WS SL:BC-Australia-Pizza Delivery Killer; CT:a; 
(REG:EURO;)
(REG:BRIT;)
(REG:SCAN;)
(REG:MEST;)
(REG:AFRI;)
(REG:INDI;)
(REG:ENGL;)
(LANG:ENGLISH;))
