<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-France-Air France Strike, Advisory. </SLUG>


<TEXT>
	   Editors. The story slugged France-Air France Strike, 2nd
Ld-Writethru that just moved on your wires should have been slugged
a 3rd Ld-Writethru.
