<HEADLINE>
UNDATED: Deborah Seward.
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; TENNIS: &QL; 

<TEXT>
	   HALLE, Germany _ French Open winner Carlos Moya and Boris Becker
see action at the Gerry Weber Open, a tuneup for Wimbledon.
	   Slug Sports-Tennis-Gerry Weber Open. Expected 1800 GMT.
	   LONDON _ After the first day was washed out by rain, defending
champion Mark Philippoussis, Goran Ivanisevic and Todd Martin are
among players in action at the Queen's Club tournament.
