	   _VATICAN-OBIT-CASAROLI. Cardinal Agostino Casaroli, the
Vatican's former No. 2 official whose cautious diplomacy helped the
church survive in Eastern Europe during Cold War years, died
Tuesday at 83.
	   FRANKFURT _ Germany's jobless rate sank below 11 percent in May
for the first time since 1996. GERMANY-UNEMPLOYMENT.
	   GENEVA _ Colombia and China were singled out for criticism over
abuses of labor union rights in a report published Tuesday to
