<SLUG> FOUR-KILLED-IN-SEPARATE sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Four killed in separate incidents in Sunamganj, THE INDEPENDENT
</HEADLINE>
Four killed in separate incidents in Sunamganj, THE INDEPENDENT &QL; 
   June 09, 1998
   THE INDEPENDENT
   BANGLADESH
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

<TEXT>
WASHINGTON, D.C. 20003 Tel: 202-547-4512 Fax: 202-546-4194
COPYRIGHT 1998 BY WORLDSOURCES, INC., A JOINT VENTURE OF FDCH, INC.
AND WORLD TIMES, INC. NO PORTION OF THE MATERIALS CONTAINED HEREIN
MAY BE USED IN ANY MEDIA WITHOUT ATTRIBUTION TO WORLDSOURCES, INC.
	   Four persons were killed in separate incidents in the district
recently.A rickshawpuller was crushed under the wheels of a
speeding truck on the Sylhet-Bianibazar road on June 4. Thana
sources said, the accident took place when a stone- laden truck
from Jafflong hit a Rickshaw from behind at 12 noon on the
Sylhet-Bianibazar road killing the rickshawpuller on the spot. The
victim, identified as Rashid, hails from village Chameshwari in
Thakurgaon district.
	   Bianibazar police seized the killer truck and arrested its
driver. Police sent the body to Sylhet Osmany Medical College
Hospital for autopsy. A case was filed in this connection. A
housewife named Jariful (24) committed suicide by taking poison at
Khadimnagar area in the town. Family sources said, Jariful took
poison in the morning on June 4 and became unconscious. She was
taken to Osmany Medical College Hospital where doctors on duty
declared her dead. A 15- year- old girl committed suicide by
hanging from the ceiling of her home at village Waiskhali in the
district on May 31.
	   The victim, idenified as Muslima Begum, daughter of Jalal Uddin
of village Jamlabaj in Sadar thana went to her aunt's house at
Waiskhazi village in the town where she committed suicide. The
victim had a love affair with a youth, it is learnt. Azmat Ali of
village Maizbari in Sadar thana committed suicide by taking poison
at about 12 noon on the same day. It is learnt that, to get rid of
chronic pain Azmat Ali committed suicide. The bodies were sent to
Sunamganj Sadar Hospital for autopsy. Two separate UD cases were
filed with Kotwali thana.
	   
</TEXT>
