<SLUG> BC-Sports-Soccer-Yugoslavia,0516 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
World Cup: Yugoslavs arrive in France with optimism and trouble
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; RETRANSMITS to fix slug &QL; 
 &UR; By DUSAN STOJANOVIC &QC; 
 &UR; Associated press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
