	   MALAYSIAN rubber prices closed lower, reflecting weak regional
prices and lack of demand.
	   June International RSS One ended at 282.00 sen per kg compared
to 285 sen on Friday while June SMR 20 closed at 270.50 per kg
compared to 273.50 sen at the end of last week.
