<HEADLINE>
Malacca town losing clean image, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Malacca town losing clean image, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
