1998 BIR-Issued Circulars, Memoranda, BUSINESS DAILY &QL; 
   June 09, 1998
   BUSINESS DAILY
   PHILIPPINES
   ENGLISH
   Vicky _ FernandezASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

