<BODY>
<SLUG> ASPEN-TOWER-TOPS sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Aspen Tower 'Tops Off', BUSINESS DAILY
</HEADLINE>
Aspen Tower 'Tops Off', BUSINESS DAILY &QL; 
   June 09, 1998
   BUSINESS DAILY
   PHILIPPINES
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

