	   Ayala Life Assurance Inc., one of the leading insurance
companies in the country, is set to inaugurate this June its
business offices at the new 14-storey Ayala Life-FGU Center
Alabang. The building serves as an elegant gateway to the fastest
growing Central Business District south of Makati, the Madrigal
Business Park. It sits on a 1,600-square meter lot strategically
located at the corner of Acacia Ave. and the Alabang-Zapote Road.
	   The new building, developed by Ayala Land, is equipped with
state of the art advanced building systems for mechanical,
plumbing, fire detection, alarm and protection, electrical and
emergency power. After full testing and commissioning, the Ayala
Life-FGU Center Alabang is now fully operational and ready for
occupancy. Its first occupant at present is the Makati Development
Corp. By end of July, Globalbank, an affiliate of Metrobank, will
occupy one of its ground floor banking halls.
	   
