(WS SL:BC-Sports-Soccer-Italy-Ravanelli, 1st Ld-Writethru; CT:s; 
(REG:EURO;)
(REG:BRIT;)
(REG:SCAN;)
(REG:MEST;)
(REG:AFRI;)
