<SLUG> BC-Sports-Tennis_DFS Classic-Results </SLUG>


<TEXT>
	   BIRMINGHAM, England (AP) _ Results of Tuesday's matches at the
DFS Classic womens grass court tournament:
 &UR; Singles &QC; 
 &UR; First Round &QC; 
	   Catalina Cristea, Romania, def. Lea Ghirardi-Rubbi, France, 3-6,
5-2, retired hurt.
	   Tatiana Panova, Russia, def. Gala Leon Garcia, Spain, 7-5, 4-6,
6-2
	   Laura Golarsa, Italy, def. Denisa Chladkova, Czech Republic,
6-3, 7-5
	   Kerry-Anne Guse, Australia, def. Amelie Cocheteux, France, 6-1,
6-3
	   Larisa Neiland, Latvia, def. Erika De Lone, United States, 6-2,
6-3
	   Mariaan De Swardt, South Africa, def. Karen Cross, Britain, 6-4,
6-1
