r w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  KRU-SOLDIERS-ONsked     06-09 0676
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> KRU-SOLDIERS-ON sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
KRU soldiers on, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
KRU soldiers on, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
   Jo LeeASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

