<SLUG> MALAYSIA sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Malaysia, BUSINESS TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Malaysia, BUSINESS TIMES &QL; 
   June 09, 1998
   BUSINESS TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

