<HEADLINE>
Toshiba announces latest VCD player, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Toshiba announces latest VCD player, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
   Subashini SelvaratnamASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

