<HEADLINE>
Enhancing clip-art graphics, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Enhancing clip-art graphics, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
